name: Redacted
description: Redacted is a multi-vertical Web3 ecosystem focused on bridging Real-World Assets (RWA) with on-chain accessibility. It powers products across RWA, DeFi, GameFi and Creator Platforms through its ecosystem token $RDAC. Following its merger with Tenset in October 2025, Redacted became the ecosystem layer uniting token launches and RWA participation under a single, scalable framework serving both institutional and retail users.
